Texts.Eng: A model of a standard human car. It's been a while since I've seen one.
Texts.Chs: 标准人类汽车的模型。我已经有一段时间没看到了。

Texts.Eng: Amazing! This human relic survived Earth!
Texts.Chs: 太神了这个人类遗物在地球上幸存了下来！

Texts.Eng: An archaic, primitive method of human transportation. This one appears to be purely for show.
Texts.Chs: 一种古老、原始的人类运输方式。这一次似乎纯粹是为了作秀。

Texts.Eng: Aw, shucks. Never got the chance to ride in one o' these...
Texts.Chs: 噢，糟了。从来没有机会坐在这些车里。。。

Texts.Eng: Floran hasn't seen one of these sssince Koala days!
Texts.Chs: 自从考拉时代以来，叶族人就再也没有见过这样的动物了！

Texts.Eng: Nonfunctional, but man - what a sight for sore eyes!
Texts.Chs: 无功能，但人-多么令人痛心的景象！

Texts.Eng: Punch buggy! ... No wait, that's for Volkswagens.
Texts.Chs: 冲床车。。。不，等等，那是给大众的。

Texts.Eng: Seems this model's for display purposes only. A shame.
Texts.Chs: 看起来这个模型只是为了展示。真可惜。
